text:
@Aktiehedonist The 3 members leaving were local Swedish/EU.
This is just a shift in strategy from focusing on developing local Swedish Semi environments:
To dominating the US/global photonics market.  New directors and new strategy for incoming NASDAQ listing this is bulish my friend.

